Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Carter's first Europe visit
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b0407cdv
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 1 May 1977
Carter to make his first official visit to Europe as US President. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.